dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Crawford County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data represent roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Crawford County, Wisconsin in 2018.
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2019. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2018. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2019.
